### 구성요소 5: 다환경 LLM 자동 라우팅

```bash
# install.sh — 스펙 자동 감지 후 적합한 모델 선택
RAM_GB=$(free -g | awk '/^Mem:/{print $2}')
GPU_VRAM=$(nvidia-smi --query-gpu=memory.total \
  --format=csv,noheader 2>/dev/null | head -1 | grep -o '[0-9]*')

if [ -n "$GPU_VRAM" ] && [ "$GPU_VRAM" -ge 8000 ]; then
    OLLAMA_MODEL="llama3.1:8b-instruct"
elif [ "$RAM_GB" -ge 16 ]; then
    OLLAMA_MODEL="llama3.1:8b-instruct-q4_K_M"
elif [ "$RAM_GB" -ge 8 ]; then
    OLLAMA_MODEL="phi3.5:3.8b-instruct-q4_K_M"
else
    echo "WARNING: RAM < 8GB. AI 분석 비활성화."
    AI_ANALYSIS_ENABLED=false
fi
```

**Ansible 환경 프로파일 (profiles/bare-metal-lowspec.yml):**
```yaml
ollama_model: "phi3.5:3.8b-instruct-q4_K_M"
ollama_gpu: false
grafana_retention_days: 30
loki_retention_days: 7
prometheus_retention: "15d"
ai_analysis_enabled: true
health_beacon_enabled: true
```

